74
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,800
Kamu semua pengkhianat!

75
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,720
Inginkah kamu memberontak?

76
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:25,800
Biadab!

77
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:29,120
Bukannya orang soleh mahu memberontak,

78
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,360
sebaliknya maharaja yang memaksa rakyat

79
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,680
memberontak.

80
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,840
Puteri Zhen membantu dunia
dan menyelamatkan rakyat,

81
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:35,240
