Beta.

106
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:18,880
Memandangkan beta

107
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,120
mahu menjadi maharaja,

108
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,520
beta perlukan orang di harem.

109
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,040
Sebelum ini,

110
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,080
Wei Wei melayan beta

111
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,200
dengan baik.

112
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:28,480
Apa kata

113
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,640
bonda mengurniakan dia kepada beta?

114
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:31,680
[Kejam!]

115
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,520
Bagi Jing Nan pula,

116
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:35,880
dia mendominasi dan angkuh sejak kecil.

117
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,520
[Beta ingin mengekalkannya di sisi beta]

118
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:38,720
[sebagai pengiring.]

119
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:40,280
[Beta akan membalas semua jasa]

120
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,080
