Dah keterlaluan ni!

124
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:48,640
-Turun!
-Jing Qing.

125
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,880
Janganlah berlebihan!

126
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,120
Awak hanyalah

127
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,120
maharaja yang dijatuhkan sekarang.

128
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,600
Beta memasukan awak ke harem beta,

129
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,840
awak patut bersyukur

130
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,480
