Memandangkan tuanku sukainya,

134
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,640
ambil sahaja.

135
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,240
Terima kasih, bonda.

136
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,440
Mari kita pergi, maharani.

137
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,320
Awak...

138
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:27,280
Maharani balu.

139
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,440
Mengapa tidak membunuhnya?

140
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,240
Lelaki sendiri

141
