mempunyai bakat luar biasa.

172
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,840
Kalau nak bunuh, bunuh saja!

173
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:05,440
Seronok main helah macam ini?

174
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,120
Lebih seronok jika awak hidup

175
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,680
dalam kesusahan.

176
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:15,840
Kamu sungguh damai.

177
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:17,880
Bonda pun lega.

178
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:22,080
Awak patut berjumpa
dengan para pembesar baharu.

179
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,480
Jangan melampau lagi.

180
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,920
Jangan terganggu urusan negara.

181
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,560
Baik, bonda.

182
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:44,560
Janganlah bertindak terburu-buru
sebelum tentera tiba.

183
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,680
Jika maharani balu marah...

184
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:49,240
Mati sahaja, apa masalahnya?

185
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,840
Cuaca elok malam ini.

186
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,680
Nak pergi jalan-jalan?

187
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,240
Saya tidak berniat menyembunyikannya.

188
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,320
Cuma bonda saya

189
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,800
menempatkan pengintip di dalam istana.

190
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,120
Awak anggap saya sebagai beban.

191
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,120
Jika bukan kerana saya,

192
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:38,000
tidak perlulah awak menghubungi mereka.

193
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,000
Jika tekaan saya betul,

194
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:54,440
orang yang nak membunuh awak secara rahsia

195
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,400
ialah bonda saya.

196
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,280
Sebaik sahaja kita melepasi cabaran ini,

197
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:58,800
semuanya akan baik-baik saja.

198
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,160
Wei Wei.

199
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:10,760
Itu...

200
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:12,240
Tentera akan tiba esok.

201
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,440
Apakah pengaturan untuk masa depan?

202
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,200
Masih perlu lari?

203
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,560
Jeneral!

204
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:19,000
Adakah sekarang masa
untuk bercakap tentang ini?

205
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,360
Tetapkan rancangan.

206
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:22,440
Kamu teruskan.

207
00:10:29,880 --> 00:10:31,880
Bilakah Jing Nan mengetahuinya?

208
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:35,080
Hanya awal sedikit daripada awak.

209
00:10:38,560 --> 00:10:39,680
Tidurlah bersendirian!

210
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,320
Baiklah.

211
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,440
Lekas pergi.

